4 HR____ COMMENDING OAKWORTH CAPITAL BANK FOR BEING RECOGNIZED
5 NINE CONSECUTIVE YEARS AS THE "BEST BANK TO WORK FOR IN THE
6 U.S."
7
8 WHEREAS, it is with great honor that we celebrate the
9 extraordinary success of Oakworth Capital Bank, with four
10 locations in the Southeast, including Alabama offices in
11 Birmingham and Mobile; and
12 WHEREAS, founded in 2008 and headquartered in
13 Birmingham, Oakworth Capital Bank has been recognized for
14 nine consecutive years by American Banker as a "Best Bank to
15 Work for in the U.S."; over that period, Oakworth has held
16 the No. 1 position six times and been ranked No. 2 in both
17 2024 and 2025; and
18 WHEREAS, this recognition is meaningful as it
19 reflects the culture that Oakworth's associates have built
20 together over time; rankings are based on survey feedback
21 measuring workplace engagement, satisfaction, and culture;
22 Oakworth's purpose is simply helping people succeed; and
23 WHEREAS, its commitment to people and purpose extends
24 beyond Oakworth's internal culture; in 2024, the
25 organization achieved a Net Promoter Score of 94, standing
26 significantly above industry averages and reflecting the
27 trust and satisfaction of both its clients and associates;
28 and
Page 1

and
HR295 INTRODUCED
29 WHEREAS, Oakworth's culture is rooted in genuine care
30 and shared respect; the energy, professionalism, and purpose
31 of its associates continue to define Oakworth's success;
32 there is an emphasis on community and a focus on doing the
33 right thing the right way every time; and
34 WHEREAS, Oakworth provides commercial and private
35 banking, wealth management, and advisory services to clients
36 across the United States; as of September 30, 2025, Oakworth
37 held $1.9 billion in total assets, $1.5 billion in gross
38 loans, $1.7 billion in deposits, and $2.6 billion in wealth
39 and trust assets under management; and
40 WHEREAS, the American Banker distinction reflects
41 positively on our state and on the many Alabama-based
42 organizations committed to building strong workplaces and
43 serving others well, and we take delight in wishing another
44 successful year to Oakworth Capital Bank; now therefore,
45 BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES OF THE
46 LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA, That the leadership and staff of
47 Oakworth Capital Bank are highly honored and commended, and
48 we hereby dedicate this resolution to them with heartiest
49 appreciation, admiration, and regard.
